  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Monastery product shop</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Caritas Finland has a shop that sells monastery products from Spain, France and Finland, thus supporting the monastic communities and raising funds for Caritas Finland activities. Some products also come from projects in developing countries, including India, Kenya and Philippines. The products are sold in our office, as well as in church bazaars, Christmas markets and various festivals, thereby raising funds to Caritas activities, making known our work to the wider public, and well as offering volunteering opportunities to our members. Many of our current members and active volunteers have found their way into Caritas through the monastery product shop.</narrative>
  </description>
